Break compulsary? No but without it expected answer ni aayega...due to fall through condition
Last case me nhi lgate break bss kyoki wha se fall direct switch ke bahar hi hoga
Default ko last mein hi likhte h isliye usmen break nhi lgate ..agr usko beech mein khi likho to lgao break

break is necessary to avoid fall through situation

Order wise likhna not zruri
